column12: Method and Apparatus for Intraoperative Monitoring of Lead Placement in Dorsal Root Ganglion Stimulation
column13: Disclosed and described here are an adapter for a neuromonitoring system for placement of an electrode in a subject and a method for confirming placement of an electrode on an appropriate nerve fiber of a dorsal root ganglion during a dorsal root ganglion stimulation procedure.
